ne globulins in persons with altered immunocompetence." MMWR Morb Mortal Wkly Rep 42(RR-04) (1993): 1-18[4] CDC. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention "Smallpox vaccination clinic guide. Logistical considerations and guidance for state and local planning for emergency, large-scale, voluntary administration of smallpox vaccine in response to a smallpox outbreak. Available from: URL: http://www.bt.cdc.gov" ([2002 Oct 16]):', 1767369485);
